text: Eteke yetiya ami chula'imanara mrtyu ghatalo, tetiya jinabilakaka te'omra mrtyu samparke aragata karaale matira parauraaya, yiborae te'omra lakhutidala kha'i achila. Phalata te'om yetiya matita bagarai paraile tetiyahe jinabilake bujiba paraile ye, yadi sihamte gayeba janilehemtena, tente sihamte lanchanadayaka sastita arad'dha nathakilehemtena
